---
import PageShell from '../../../../components/PageShell.astro';
import CTABox from '../../../../components/CTABox.astro';
import ComparisonTable from '../../../../components/ComparisonTable.astro';

const tocItems = [
  { id: 'overview', text: 'AXA Global in Panama', level: 2 },
  { id: 'why-axa', text: 'Why AXA for Panama', level: 2 },
  { id: 'plans-and-pricing', text: 'Plans and Pricing', level: 2 },
  { id: 'coverage-details', text: 'Coverage Details', level: 2 },
  { id: 'who-its-for', text: 'Who Should Consider AXA', level: 2 },
];

const relatedLinks = [
  { title: 'Health Insurance in Panama', href: '/countries/panama/insurance' },
  { title: 'AXA Global Review', href: '/providers/axa-global' },
  { title: 'AXA vs Cigna', href: '/compare/axa-global-vs-cigna-global' },
];

const planColumns = [
  { key: 'plan', header: 'Plan' },
  { key: 'coverage', header: 'Coverage' },
  { key: 'price', header: 'Price (Age 55)' },
];

const planRows = [
  { plan: 'Standard', coverage: 'Core inpatient', price: '$220-300/mo' },
  { plan: 'Comfort', coverage: 'Inpatient + outpatient', price: '$300-400/mo' },
  { plan: 'Comprehensive', coverage: 'Full coverage', price: '$380-500/mo' },
];
---

<PageShell
  title="AXA Global Health Insurance in Panama"
  description="Guide to AXA Global international health insurance for expats in Panama. European insurer with global reach and solid coverage options."
  headline="AXA Global in Panama"
  subheadline="Major European insurer with worldwide coverage. Solid option for Panama expats seeking established international protection."
  heroBackgroundImage="/images/countries/panama-hero-bg.png"
  tocItems={tocItems}
  relatedLinks={relatedLinks}
  ctaButtonText="Get an AXA Quote"
  ctaButtonHref="/go/axa-global"
>
  <h2 id="overview">AXA Global in Panama</h2>
  <p>
    AXA is one of the world's largest insurance groups, headquartered in France with operations spanning the globe. For Panama expats, AXA Global Healthcare offers established international health insurance with strong financial backing.
  </p>
  <p>
    While perhaps less well-known among American retirees than US-based competitors, AXA provides solid coverage and competitive options for expats from various backgrounds.
  </p>

  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 my-8">
    <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-4 text-center">
      <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-600">$250-420</p>
      <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600">Monthly (Age 55)</p>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-4 text-center">
      <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-600">Global</p>
      <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600">Insurance leader</p>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-4 text-center">
      <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-600">European</p>
      <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600">Headquarters</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <CTABox
    title="Get Your AXA Panama Quote"
    description="Global coverage from an established insurer."
    buttonText="Get Quote"
    buttonHref="/go/axa-global"
    variant="highlight"
  />

  <h2 id="why-axa">Why AXA for Panama</h2>

  <h3>Financial Strength</h3>
  <p>
    AXA Group is one of the largest insurers globally:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>Operations in 50+ countries</li>
    <li>Strong financial ratings</li>
    <li>Long-term stability for retirees</li>
    <li>Reliable claims payment history</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>International Network</h3>
  <p>
    AXA has built extensive provider networks worldwide:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>Relationships with Panama's private hospitals</li>
    <li>Global coverage for travel</li>
    <li>Direct billing in many locations</li>
    <li>24/7 multilingual assistance</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>European Expat Friendly</h3>
  <p>
    For European expats in Panama, AXA's European headquarters and approach may feel familiar. Customer service, documentation, and processes align with European expectations.
  </p>

  <div class="bg-blue-50 border border-blue-200 rounded-lg p-6 my-6">
    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-blue-900 mb-3">Good Alternative</h3>
    <p class="text-blue-800">
      If you're comparing options beyond the typical US-focused insurers, AXA provides a solid alternative with competitive pricing and comprehensive coverage. Worth including in your comparison.
    </p>
  </div>

  <h2 id="plans-and-pricing">Plans and Pricing</h2>

  <div class="my-8 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
    <ComparisonTable columns={planColumns} rows={planRows} />
  </div>

  <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600 italic">
    Prices shown for healthy 55-year-old. Actual premiums depend on age, health status, and coverage selections.
  </p>

  <h3>Plan Structure</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Standard:</strong> Hospital and emergency coverage, evacuation included</li>
    <li><strong>Comfort:</strong> Adds outpatient care, specialists, diagnostic coverage</li>
    <li><strong>Comprehensive:</strong> Full coverage including wellness, enhanced mental health</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Area of Coverage</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Americas:</strong> Most affordable for Panama-based expats</li>
    <li><strong>Worldwide excluding US:</strong> Good for those who travel globally but don't need US coverage</li>
    <li><strong>Worldwide:</strong> Full global coverage including US (highest premium)</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 id="coverage-details">Coverage Details</h2>

  <h3>What's Covered</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Inpatient:</strong> Hospital stays, surgery, intensive care, rehabilitation</li>
    <li><strong>Outpatient:</strong> Doctor visits, specialists, tests (Comfort+)</li>
    <li><strong>Emergency:</strong> Worldwide emergency treatment</li>
    <li><strong>Evacuation:</strong> Medical evacuation and repatriation</li>
    <li><strong>Cancer:</strong> Comprehensive cancer treatment coverage</li>
    <li><strong>Chronic conditions:</strong> Coverage with appropriate management</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Optional Modules</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Dental coverage</li>
    <li>Optical/vision coverage</li>
    <li>Maternity benefits</li>
    <li>Wellness and preventive care</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Limitations</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Pre-existing conditions: Subject to underwriting</li>
    <li>Waiting periods: Some benefits have waiting periods</li>
    <li>Mental health: Limits apply in most plans</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 id="who-its-for">Who Should Consider AXA</h2>

  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 my-8">
    <div class="bg-green-50 border border-green-200 rounded-lg p-6">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-green-900 mb-3">Good Fit</h3>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-green-800">
        <li>European expats</li>
        <li>Those seeking established insurers</li>
        <li>Expats comparing multiple options</li>
        <li>Those not needing US coverage</li>
        <li>Long-term Panama residents</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">May Prefer Alternatives</h3>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-neutral-600">
        <li>Americans wanting BCBS access</li>
        <li>Those with existing US insurer relationships</li>
        <li>Those needing extensive US coverage</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h3>Age-Related Pricing</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Age 55:</strong> $250-420/month</li>
    <li><strong>Age 65:</strong> $380-600/month</li>
    <li><strong>Age 75:</strong> $530-800/month</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Pre-existing Conditions</h3>
  <p>
    AXA offers several approaches:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Moratorium:</strong> Pre-existing conditions excluded for defined period</li>
    <li><strong>Full medical underwriting:</strong> Individual assessment of conditions</li>
    <li>Some plans may offer medical history disregarded options at higher premium</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Customer Service</h3>
  <p>
    AXA provides multilingual support and has regional offices that understand Latin American healthcare systems, which can be valuable for Panama-based members.
  </p>

  <CTABox
    title="Compare AXA Plans for Panama"
    description="Global insurer, comprehensive coverage."
    buttonText="Get Quote"
    buttonHref="/go/axa-global"
    variant="highlight"
  />

  <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6 mt-8">
    <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600">
      <strong>Disclaimer:</strong> Prices and coverage are estimates. Contact AXA for accurate quotes based on your specific needs and circumstances.
    </p>
  </div>
</PageShell>
